These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, librarian, coach, dressmaker
1. the librarian is in an odd position##4
2. the dressmaker is between the analyst and the librarian##2
3. the dressmaker is on the right of the analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Job   | analyst | dressmaker | librarian | coach |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, scientific, animation, superhero
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | comedy | superhero | animation |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, swimming, golf, baseball
1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
2. the person who's sport is badminton is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's sport is golf is between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who's sport is swimming##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Sport   | badminton | baseball | golf | swimming |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, house, pop, indie
1. the fan of house is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
2. the fan of pop is in an even position##4
3. the fan of indie is between the fan of funk and the fan of pop##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | house | funk | indie | pop |

