.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, cycling, skiing, cricket
1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
3. the person who's sport is skiing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3   |    4    |
| Sport   | skiing | tennis | cricket | cycling |

