.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-7::.
4 different pets are kept: goat, cat, dog, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the dog is between the owner of the goat and the owner of the cat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |    2    |      3      |     4      |
| Pet   | guinea-pig | goat | dog | cat |

