.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-12::.
City: london, venice, new-york, hannover
1. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
2. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
3. the person traveling to venice is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |  3  |    4    |
| City   | new-york | venice | hannover | london |

