.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-14::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, water, cola
1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
3. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
4. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | water | cola | almond-milk | hot-chocolate |

