.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-15::.
House: tower, townhouse, cottage, cape-cod
1. the cottage house is on the right of the tower house##1
2. the townhouse house is in an even position##4
3. the tower house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1      |   2    |    3     |    4     |
| House   | cape-cod | tower | cottage | townhouse |

