.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-16::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, february, april, august
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|        |  1   |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Birthday   | march | february | april | august |

