.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, fuchsia, brown, pink
1. the person who likes fuchsia is the person who likes fuchsia##1
2. the person who likes pink is on the left or right of the person who likes brown##3
3. the person who likes brown is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who likes grey is in an even position##4
5. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Color   | brown | pink | fuchsia | grey |

