.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-20::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, december, january, april
1. the person who's birthday is in january is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |         2          |    3    |    4     |
| Birthday   | september | april | january | december |

 